EN: The subway network is very developed in the city.

ZH: 我宁愿坐地铁也不愿开车。
EN: I would rather take the subway than drive.

ZH: 刚刚赶上了最后一班地铁。
EN: I just caught the last subway train.

ZH: 坐地铁比坐公交更快捷。
EN: Taking the subway is faster than taking the bus.

ZH: 地铁站周围的商业区生意兴隆。
EN: The business district around the subway station is thriving.

ZH: 我在地铁上看书，让时间变得有意义。
EN: I read a book on the subway to make my time meaningful.

ZH: 在地铁上保持耐心非常重要。
EN: Patience is important when riding the subway.

ZH: 地铁是有效减少交通拥堵的方式。
EN: The subway is an effective way to reduce traffic congestion.

ZH: 地铁系统在日本非常发达。
EN: The subway system in Japan is very developed.

ZH: 上班高峰期地铁总是拥挤不堪。
EN: The subway is always crowded during rush hour.

