EN: The subway is a convenient and fast mode of transportation.

ZH: 昨天晚上地铁晚点了半小时。
EN: The subway was delayed for half an hour last night.

ZH: 我不喜欢挤地铁，总是选择其他交通方式。
EN: I don't like crowding on the subway, so I always choose another mode of transportation.

